"Sorry, network access failed!

Please click Retry button to try to re-connect, if still fails, follow these steps to try to solve the problem:
1.Please make sure the modem or HUB is on;
2.Make sure broadband modem phone line or network cable is plugged in tight;
3.Make sure broadband modem DSL or LINK light is lit;
4.Restart broadband modem, pending LINK DSL light is no longer flashing lights or after the restart STB;
5.If you press above operation, the problem is not resolved, call the 10000–4–2 customer service."

